'From Squeak2.6 of 13 October 1999 [latest update: #1704] on 8 December 1999 at 4:07:43 pm'!"Change Set:		EnvFix-arDate:			8 December 1999Author:			Andreas RaabFixes a problem with infinite recursions from environments printing."!!SystemDictionary methodsFor: 'printing' stamp: 'ar 12/8/1999 16:05'!printOn: aStream	"ar 12/8/1999: Break infinite recursions"	aStream nextPutAll: self class name; nextPutAll:'(lots of globals)'! !